init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And then they had a press conference.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They were looking for him in the woods.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They found his pants, and then found the same pants again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I think we should stop looking for him and just wait for him to come back," said Ben Affleck.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was Matt Damon! "Matt Damon!" they all shouted.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm Matt Damon!" shouted the Matt Damon from the second tree.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and shot the Matt Damon from the first tree.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: he turned to the other Matt Damon and shot him too.
